data.description: Discover your dream home in the heart of the vibrant Clovis community. This immaculate residence boasts modern comforts, including a newer roof, water heater and energy-efficient dual pane windows. The leased solar, installed in 2022, ensures both sustainability and savings. Step inside to find an inviting layout with two spacious living rooms and a charming dining area, perfect for both relaxation and entertainment. With 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, which includes a master bedroom with ample space for luxury. Enjoy outdoor living under the patio cover and on the wood patio decking, overlooking the pristine pool enveloped by a potential grass area. Privacy is paramount with no rear neighbors, allowing you to relish your outdoor oasis undisturbed. This home seamlessly combines comfort, style, and practicality, making it an exceptional find in a sought-after neighborhood.
